reviewText: As a small boy I used to live in El Paso  for a few years . I fell In love with the desert and all its wild life and fauna . Love this DVD . Reminds me of my child hood days in El Paso .
Although a bit "dated", this is still a very interesting NAT GEO special about the worlds deserts.  I was glad that this was formated to DVD as I no longer have a VHS Player.
